Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.98,0:00:08.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm happy! I'm happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.92,0:00:11.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow is going\Nto be a fun Sunday!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.69,0:00:13.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,And I have free\Ntickets to Aqualand!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.20,0:00:19.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,All right! I'm going to ask\NHaneoka for a date! Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.68,0:00:23.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy...!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.52,0:00:30.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Haneoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.43,0:00:32.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.01,0:00:36.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,They're cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.57,0:00:39.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What's up, Sawatari?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.55,0:00:41.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.82,0:00:44.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,There are two beautiful girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.82,0:00:46.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,And they're stunning\Nin their summer school uniforms.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.03,0:00:50.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,One shines like gold\Nin the summer sun...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.47,0:00:52.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,She's like a sunflower.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.27,0:00:57.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,The other sits quietly\Nin the heart of the forest...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.31,0:00:59.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,She is like a white lily...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.35,0:01:03.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Oh, do I have to choose one?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.13,0:01:08.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Am I going to break up\Ntheir friendship?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.40,0:01:09.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,No, I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.74,0:01:14.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Lord, please forgive my sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.81,0:01:18.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,And please show this\Nlost sheep the right way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.65,0:01:22.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Five free tickets?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.19,0:01:23.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for getting enough\Ntickets to include me, Saruwatari.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.33,0:01:28.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That's right! I have five tickets.\NSo all three of can them can go...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.87,0:01:30.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Asuka Jr.\NWhat do you have?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.31,0:01:33.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Free tickets to Aqualand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.15,0:01:35.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,- Here.\N- Wow! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.58,0:01:37.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I feel bad taking these\Nfrom you, Sawatari.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.19,0:01:39.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.26,0:01:41.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,- What are you talking about?!\N- Don't hang on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.20,0:01:43.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Wow! A free ticket to Aqualand!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.53,0:01:45.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,If you're going, I'm going, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.50,0:01:47.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hold on for just a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.87,0:01:50.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,First of all, there are\Nonly five free tickets!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.69,0:01:58.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Wow, perfect! Did you\Nhave something to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.06,0:02:00.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,No... Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.20,0:02:06.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,"WHITE DOLPHIN"\N- RETURN TO THE SEA!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.63,0:02:19.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,As usual, there's\Na big Sunday crowd!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.84,0:02:21.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Everyone! This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.64,0:02:22.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,They said the aquarium\Nis on the third floor...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.91,0:02:23.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...and we need to use an elevator!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.04,0:02:25.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.86,0:02:35.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if we could\Nget on the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.46,0:02:36.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I guess we can get on somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.57,0:02:39.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.21,0:02:41.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,We're going up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.28,0:02:43.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.18,0:02:45.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,We just made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.93,0:02:52.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! How embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.83,0:02:53.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.60,0:02:58.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,We can easily\Nsqueeze in one more!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.55,0:03:03.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What was that?!\NDid I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.46,0:03:09.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.87,0:03:13.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,My hand...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.61,0:03:17.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Shoot! I didn't let go of her hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.58,0:03:22.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You two!\NYou're too close to each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.62,0:03:23.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Break it up! Break it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.06,0:03:26.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous!\NIt's just the situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.90,0:03:27.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Good grief!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.38,0:03:35.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.71,0:03:38.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Get there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.29,0:03:40.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Come on, third floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.96,0:03:47.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Second floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.80,0:03:48.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Going up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.00,0:03:49.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,No! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.18,0:03:54.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.52,0:04:00.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Just the two of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.43,0:04:05.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What?! We lost Haneoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.84,0:04:07.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Asuka, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.21,0:04:11.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! I thought we were going\Nto have an enjoyable day together!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.35,0:04:14.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,She must be alone\Nand crying right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.95,0:04:16.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Asuka is with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.59,0:04:18.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Is this by any chance\Na kidnapping...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.69,0:04:21.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I told you, Asuka is with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.40,0:04:24.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Haneoka! I, Manato Sawatari,\Nam on my way to save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.24,0:04:27.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You're not listening...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.48,0:04:28.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.98,0:04:32.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,If we go slowly now,\Nthey'll catch up with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.79,0:04:33.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.03,0:04:39.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Yes! You're absolutely right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.10,0:04:41.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,He sure is quick\Nat switching his attention...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.61,0:04:46.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,This is a great opportunity.\NI want them to be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.31,0:04:47.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I call this plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.38,0:04:50.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Seira's Love Love Strategy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.59,0:04:52.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it great?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.69,0:04:55.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Well, Mimori?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.53,0:04:57.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Let's go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.50,0:04:58.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You're right. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.64,0:04:59.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.74,0:05:02.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Don't leave me alone! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.82,0:05:09.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I guess they already went in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.09,0:05:12.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's because I forced myself\Ninto the crowded elevator...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.90,0:05:15.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,So you wanted to be\Nseparated and all alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.07,0:05:17.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.28,0:05:22.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Why do we always\Nend up like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.75,0:05:28.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Sawatari, what do you think of fish?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.16,0:05:30.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.06,0:05:33.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I love fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.60,0:05:35.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Really? I'm glad to hear that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.08,0:05:38.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,- Sawatari.\N- Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.05,0:05:41.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you like\Nto breathe underwater?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.59,0:05:44.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Because it looks like\Nit feels good, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.60,0:05:49.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,She's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.87,0:05:50.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.27,0:05:53.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I, Sawatari, for you, Mimori...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.31,0:05:55.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...will master breathing\Nunderwater or anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.28,0:05:56.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You name it and I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.58,0:05:58.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Wow, wonderful!\NI can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.67,0:06:13.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Why do things turn out this way...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.31,0:06:30.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.69,0:06:38.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,- Well...\N- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.33,0:06:42.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I spoke with St. Tail\Nup close the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.91,0:06:50.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.75,0:06:52.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's not a good idea\Nto bring up that incident!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.39,0:06:53.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I have to change the subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.19,0:06:58.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Why do you chase her\Nso passionately?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.60,0:06:59.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,She's my dream girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.83,0:07:00.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.57,0:07:03.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no... I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.47,0:07:05.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I want to see\Nif she's my dream girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.35,0:07:08.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm curious about\Nwhat she's normally like...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.52,0:07:09.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,And many other things...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.65,0:07:14.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad...\NI'm glad it is dark... But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.53,0:07:17.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,But I continue to hide my identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.57,0:07:21.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's the same as lying to Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.31,0:07:25.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Resemble...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.42,0:07:27.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I can tell because\Nit was dark then, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.55,0:07:30.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's not her physical shape,\Nit's more her aura...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.59,0:07:33.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,She resembles Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.84,0:07:37.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.17,0:07:39.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.68,0:07:42.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What are you daydreaming about?\NYou're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.05,0:07:44.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.68,0:07:46.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,If we don't watch the fish carefully,\Nit would seem rude to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.22,0:07:50.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,There's a creepy one! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.63,0:07:53.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,- Hey! Don't pull!\N- Hurry up! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.17,0:07:54.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Look, it's a white dolphin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.72,0:08:06.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,He looks like he's having\Na conversation with the dolphin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.23,0:08:08.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Seira...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.60,0:08:09.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.14,0:08:14.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Mana...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.18,0:08:20.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,This is the Director's Office.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.62,0:08:24.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Director. That kid is glued\Nto the dolphin's glass again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.20,0:08:26.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.70,0:08:28.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,This is enough! Kick him out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.60,0:08:31.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What an annoying brat...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.45,0:08:42.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Then that white dolphin\Nis your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.16,0:08:46.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Her name is Mana.\NDo you know about Mana, Sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.94,0:08:51.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I do. I also saw you\Nat the aquarium the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.91,0:08:53.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,The director\Nof the aquarium said...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.18,0:08:56.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...that Mana was sick\Nand he could heal her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.79,0:09:00.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,He lied to me\Nand took Mana from the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.86,0:09:03.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Mana wasn't sick...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.20,0:09:23.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,He never had any intention\Nof returning Mana.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.74,0:09:26.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's because Mana is a rare breed\Ncalled a Pearl Dolphin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.41,0:09:31.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I've asked him many times\Nto return Mana, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.39,0:09:33.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,He refused, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.26,0:09:35.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Did you talk to the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.83,0:09:37.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's no use, Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.50,0:09:40.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Mana isn't my pet.\NShe's my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.34,0:09:43.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm not her owner\Nso I can't go to the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.51,0:09:45.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,The director tells me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.05,0:09:48.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...to show some evidence\Nthat Mana and I are friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.49,0:09:51.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,But it's impossible\Nbecause Mana can't speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.86,0:09:53.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Cheer up, Hiromi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.16,0:09:56.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure God will help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.14,0:09:59.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That's terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.47,0:10:00.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me, Hiromi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.78,0:10:03.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,The mysterious thief\NSt. Tail will get back Mana.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.02,0:10:08.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi says Mana can do\Na trick only when Hiromi calls her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.09,0:10:12.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Well, then...\NIf he shows it to the owner...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.13,0:10:14.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...he can prove they're friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.80,0:10:15.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,But Mana is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.87,0:10:17.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...so shocked from being\Ntaken away from the sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.34,0:10:20.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...that she has\Nbecome very depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.75,0:10:23.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,And she has been\Nin that tank for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.65,0:10:25.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,So it is impossible\Nfor her to do the trick...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.66,0:10:26.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.36,0:10:48.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I heard...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.63,0:10:51.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...Asuka had a good time\Non Sunday, right, Yasuhiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.74,0:10:53.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That's what I heard, Chiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.78,0:10:57.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I heard he had girls\Nwith him, Yasuhiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.15,0:11:00.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I envy him, Chiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.69,0:11:03.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Boy! How pesky can you two be?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.56,0:11:05.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Sawatari had free tickets.\NWhat was I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.30,0:11:08.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,If you have a problem,\Ntalk to Sawatari.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.30,0:11:11.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That's not the point.\NWhy didn't you at least tell us?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.37,0:11:12.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You're rude to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.89,0:11:22.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.36,0:11:24.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,"Tonight I'm going to Aqualand...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.93,0:11:26.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...to get the 'Pearl Dolphin.'"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.87,0:11:29.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's St. Tail's warning note!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.48,0:11:32.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What's the Pearl Dolphin?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.71,0:11:33.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.88,0:11:36.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's the white dolphin at Aqualand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.96,0:11:39.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,We've never been to Aqualand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.83,0:11:42.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It must be a beautiful dolphin.\NRight, Asuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.90,0:11:44.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You two are really\Ngetting on my nerves...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.80,0:11:46.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.72,0:11:54.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,- Hi, Meimi.\N- Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.99,0:11:55.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.13,0:11:57.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What did you do, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.53,0:11:59.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it romantic?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.50,0:12:01.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's the illusion I'm going to use\Nin the next magic show.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.24,0:12:07.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's like we're really in the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.78,0:12:09.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Dad, can you change it\Nto the sea next?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.82,0:12:11.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Of course. Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.39,0:12:16.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Wow! It brings back\Nmemories of our dates.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.10,0:12:19.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. We went\Nto the sea often, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.68,0:12:27.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.06,0:12:34.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.47,0:12:37.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.88,0:12:43.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.54,0:12:56.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Meimi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.81,0:12:59.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I think Hiromi will\Nprobably be at the aquarium.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.08,0:13:01.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.32,0:13:02.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.99,0:13:08.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,May the blessings\Nof God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.82,0:13:21.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,This is our Pearl Dolphin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.85,0:13:23.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Please protect her\Nfrom the mysterious thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.16,0:13:25.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,- Yes!\N- Put me down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.53,0:13:28.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Put me down!\NReturn Mana! You liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.00,0:13:30.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That kid again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.54,0:13:31.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.47,0:13:34.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You're still here?!\NIt's way past closing time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.01,0:13:35.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Director.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.65,0:13:38.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Like I've told you before...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.15,0:13:41.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...there's no proof\Nthat the dolphin is your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.69,0:13:45.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Mana will flip in the air\Nat my command. I'm not lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.47,0:13:49.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe it.\NShe hasn't been trained.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.74,0:13:51.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,If you're too persistent,\NI'll report you to the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.05,0:13:53.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's true! Believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.55,0:13:56.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Then have her do the trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.89,0:13:59.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,If she does the trick,\NI'll let her go back to the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.23,0:14:02.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Really? Will you really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.00,0:14:04.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.50,0:14:06.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's a promise between two men.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.57,0:14:10.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,But I don't think the dolphin\Ncan do a flip from the tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.08,0:14:12.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.79,0:14:14.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Kick him out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.06,0:14:16.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,- Yes!\N- Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.56,0:14:19.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Bad news! St. Tail showed up\Non the surveillance camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.63,0:14:20.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.01,0:14:28.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.65,0:14:31.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Good evening, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.72,0:14:34.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,The St. Tail dolphin show...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.56,0:14:36.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...will be starting\Nat the dolphin's stage shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.23,0:14:40.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Tonight's special guest\Nis the Pearl Dolphin, Mana.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.87,0:14:43.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.78,0:14:45.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.45,0:14:48.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,How could this be...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.82,0:14:49.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,How did she open...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.96,0:14:51.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...the gate between\Nthe tank and the stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.66,0:14:54.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,- Let's go!\N- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.54,0:15:02.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Here we are. Get off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.99,0:15:11.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.13,0:15:14.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Mana...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.42,0:15:28.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Return Mana! You liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.60,0:15:32.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Mana will flip in the air\Nat my command. I'm not lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.14,0:15:36.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Tonight's special guest\Nis the Pearl Dolphin, Mana.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.12,0:15:40.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Hiromi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.89,0:15:43.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Mana is at the dolphin stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.79,0:15:46.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.24,0:15:56.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Mana looks depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.48,0:15:57.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.45,0:16:00.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Mana!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.69,0:16:01.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.23,0:16:04.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Mana!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.23,0:16:07.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Mana! Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.27,0:16:11.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.11,0:16:14.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What's going on, Asuka Jr.?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.15,0:16:17.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Get St. Tail now! Otherwise...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.69,0:16:19.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise... what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.59,0:16:21.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,The dolphin will do a flip?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.16,0:16:24.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I won't ask you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.30,0:16:26.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Mana!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.37,0:16:28.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.48,0:16:30.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Jump, Mana! Mana!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.32,0:16:34.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,If you don't jump,\Nyou can't go back to the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.99,0:16:36.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Where's the flip?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.36,0:16:42.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,If she doesn't jump,\NI can't return her to the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.34,0:16:44.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.01,0:16:48.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Because you lied\Nand put her in the tank...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.45,0:16:50.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...now she's really sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.95,0:16:52.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That's enough, brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.62,0:16:54.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.99,0:16:55.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Mana!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.16,0:16:57.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.27,0:17:00.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'll make you keep\Nthe promise with Hiromi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.87,0:17:01.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.95,0:17:07.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.75,0:17:12.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...Show...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.43,0:17:14.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.55,0:17:28.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Mana!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.69,0:17:31.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Open your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.30,0:17:33.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You're in the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.09,0:17:45.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Mana...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.62,0:17:47.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.56,0:17:49.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...the fun time you spent...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.23,0:17:50.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...with Hiromi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.30,0:17:52.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Remember the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.64,0:17:55.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.07,0:17:57.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Mana! Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.26,0:18:06.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Mana!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.63,0:18:08.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Now you can go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.37,0:18:11.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You can go back to the sea, Mana.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.84,0:18:13.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I don't know about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.21,0:18:17.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I don't know anything\Nabout the promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.55,0:18:19.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Take the dolphin back\Nto the tank immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.05,0:18:21.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,No, Director.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.02,0:18:24.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You definitely promised!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.53,0:18:26.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I am a witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.87,0:18:28.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's not a pretty picture\Nyou're painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.14,0:18:31.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Shoot...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.64,0:18:32.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.15,0:18:36.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Asuka Jr.! St. Tail is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.42,0:18:40.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Wait! St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.49,0:18:43.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Take care of the rest, Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.13,0:18:45.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you to wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.34,0:18:49.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I have to catch you\Nno matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.84,0:18:51.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.62,0:18:56.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Because I'm your dream girl...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.49,0:18:59.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,If you say it just one more time...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.16,0:19:01.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.90,0:19:04.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You resemble...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.44,0:19:07.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.71,0:19:10.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,...resemble the girl\NI can't stop thinking about!
